  "description": "<i>The Invaders: Space Invaders 1500</i> consists of all content of <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/game/space-invaders-2000\">Space Invaders 2000</a> but adds one extra game mode: <i>Space Invaders 3D</i>. Space Invaders 3D is as one would expect a three dimensional remake, but of <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/game/space-invaders-part-ii\">Space Invaders: Part II</a> and not the original <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/search/quick?game=Space+Invaders\">Space Invaders</a>. It features wireframe-style graphics and a perspective similar to <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/game/space-invaders-virtual-collection\">Space Invaders: Virtual Collection</a>. By default it's viewed from behind the shoulder of the laser gun but it is possible to change it to a closer or more distant view. A first person perspective is also possible. ",
